lead_paragraph: Japan's Kei Nishikori survived an early scare before he dispatched buccaneering Frenchman Julien Benneteau 4-6 6-4 6-4 6-2 in the Wimbledon second round on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Nishikori Survives Scare to Overpower Benneteau
